      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">The woodworking workshop is full of words that score well in Scrabble. CHISEL delivers 11 points with its CH combination, DOWEL uses the W tile efficiently, and LATHE provides a clean 8 points from 5 tiles. These are practical words everyone knows — tools you'd find in any garage.</p>
