        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🗜️ CLAMP</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">11 pts · C=3, L=1, A=1, M=3, P=3 · Holding device</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🪚 TENON</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">5 pts · T=1, E=1, N=1, O=1, N=1 · Joint projection</p></div>
